==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: eightvo
<hw>eightvo</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>the size of a book (ca. 16 x 23 cm)
whose pages are made by folding a sheet of paper three times to form
eight leaves. The pages have about half the area of a
<contr>quarto</contr>. Symbolized as <altname>8vo</altname>, and
<altname>8⟦deg⟧</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> octavo, 8vo, 8⟦deg⟧.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Eighty</ent>⟦br⟧
